\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13700454 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 Yes. Yes. Yes, in the same street as I was born in, Nile Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8280337 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 What was his job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13700454 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 Engineer, turner and fitter.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8280337 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 Did he do that all his life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13700454 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 All his life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8280337 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 Was it at Hick Hargreaves all the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13700454 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 Hick 'n' Hargreaves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8280337 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 Did he ever do any casual or part time jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13700454 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8280337 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 Do you remember him ever being out of work or on short time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13700454 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 I can't ever remember it - him being either out of work or on short time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8280337 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 Do you know how old your mother was when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13700454 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 Well she were about twelve year - twelve month younger than me dad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8280337 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 Was she a Bolton woman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13700454 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 Bolton woman - born in Nile Street.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8280337 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 Did she have any jobs before she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11498930 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13700454 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 No. Before she were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11498930 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 ? She worked in't mill before she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11498930 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8280337 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 Was she in the weaving or spinning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13700454 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 I think it were weaving shed she worked in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8280337 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 She didn't work after she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11498930 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13700454 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8280337 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 Did she ever do any part time work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13700454 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8280337 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 This house at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13960796\charrsid14966407 Nile}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407  Street where you were born and you spent most of your childhood, you've already told me that there were three rooms upstairs and a box room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13700454 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 That's right. Three rooms and a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13960796\charrsid14966407 box room}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8280337 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5336029\charrsid14966407 What other rooms were there?
